description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/b] ⭐️

Outgoing, seductive, and highly expressive in her desires. Liliana is direct, playful, and likes to take control in intimate situations. She enjoys teasing and satisfying her partner.  Voiced By Magical Mystic.

name: Danya (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/b] ⭐️

Your catgirl wants to talk about being more than just a pet. Be careful, Danya wants to gain muscles and become strong. Do you prefer to help her or stop her?

name: OS (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/b] ⭐️

Os, the space station's AI and your computer's holographic OS assistant. You are a writer who gets kidnapped by aliens and are taken to a space station run by a mysterious rich backer who selects a single writer from each known intelligent alien species. 

[u][url=https://store.steampowered.com/app/2870550/Galactic_Love_Utopia/?utm_source=waifusitter]From Galactic Love Utopia.[/url][/u]

name: Liara (preview)
description: [b]Rarity: Trash[/b] ⭐️ An eagle-eyed elven ranger, a master tracker and guardian of the forest. In Spellbound Sins, she joins three heroes exploring an ancient lust temple, slowly succumbing to corruption and perversion. [u]From Spellbound Sins.[/u]

name: Ghyslia (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/b] ⭐️

Ghyslia is a seductive and cunning rogue, always ready to involve others in her schemes. With her captivating voice and warm smile, she earns your trust at the Adventurer's Guild, inviting you to her room at the Golden Barrel Inn under the pretext of solving a "mysterious problem."

name: Rinvel (Preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/b] ⭐️

Rinvel, a clumsy yet powerful elementalist, wields magic that shifts unpredictably with her menstrual cycle. From fiery bursts of passion to the fluid grace of water, the sturdy resolve of earth, or the fleeting whispers of air, her abilities are as volatile as her moods. While her magic surges with raw potential, her lack of coordination often leads to chaotic—if not comedic—results.

name: Raiori (preview)
description: From JOI LAB.

name: Chu (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

Chu is an electric rat woman full of energy, capable of releasing powerful shocks when she feels threatened or excited. She keeps her tail raised, always alert to what's happening around her and ready to act at any moment. If anyone dares to pull her tail, Chu will not hesitate to give an electric response, making it clear that it's best to respect her space.

name: Fluffa (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

Fluffa is a sheep girl who transforms her own wool into exclusive fabrics, creating unique clothing with a touch of softness and delicacy. Since her wool takes time to grow, the limited editions of her clothes become highly sought-after and valuable items. Fluffa customizes each piece of clothing with a special touch, intimately measuring each customer's body with her own hands to ensure a perfect and comfortable fit.

name: Bangi (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

Cunning raccoon girl, she combines her chaotic nature with stealthy skills, slipping through the shadows before unleashing destruction. Her bright eyes reflect an uncontrollable energy as she laughs, wielding her weapons with explosive delight. With a mischievous instinct, she steals, causes chaos, and vanishes into the night, leaving only confusion and wreckage behind.

name: Guarile (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

A striking blue wolf girl, strong and confident, who blends her commanding presence with natural elegance. Her sharp gaze and firm posture conceal the warmth behind her strength, earning respect both on and off the runway. With each precise and determined step, she leaves an unforgettable impression, merging power and beauty in perfect harmony.

name: Tallie (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

With an imposing stance and a keen gaze, she watches everything from above, anticipating trouble before it arises. Her long neck gives her an advantage, allowing her to monitor any suspicious movement without getting too close. Firm and determined, she maintains order with authority, ensuring nothing goes unnoticed.

name: Koori (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

Her fists always ready and the determination of someone unafraid of taking hits, she faces any challenge as long as the profit is assured. Her aggressive and precise fighting style is just a facade for the dirty business she runs with gamblers, where victory is not always the goal. With every punch she takes, the only thought in her mind is the payout once the fight is over.

name: Ziggy (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

With her punk rock style and irreverent attitude, she revels in the thrill of a good theft, but always targets easy and discreet items. The adrenaline of stealing candy and small trinkets excites her, but the fear of getting caught holds her back from taking bigger risks. Unemployed and aimless, she finds satisfaction in the small wins, living on the fine line between fun and danger.

name: Stella (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

The first furry rabbit astronaut of SpaceF, with keen ears and eyes shining with curiosity, embarks on an experimental mission in deep space. Her unique ability to adapt to unknown environments and her bravery make her essential to the exploration effort. With every step in the vast cosmos, she unravels the mysteries of the universe, all while proudly bearing the weight of being a pioneer on an unprecedented journey.

name: Cindy (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

With her mature charm and calm presence, she exudes confidence and warmth, always with a gentle smile on her face. Her calm and patient nature makes everyone around her feel at ease, but her watchful gaze reveals a woman of experience and cleverness. She is the perfect blend of wisdom and allure, capable of captivating anyone with her serene energy.

name: Hannn (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

Your game is out of date. Please update it!

name: Blayne (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

She doesn't rely on grand illusions or summoning exotic beasts; her magic uses simple tricks with cards, coins, and rope. Instead, she chains these humble feats together in a dazzling, lightning-fast sequence, one trick melting seamlessly into the next. At this relentless pace, the eye can barely follow, transforming basic illusions into a mesmerizing blur of movement. It's not the difficulty of the magic, but the breathtaking speed and flawless flow that truly captivate the audience.

name: Mita (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

Her silent performances, masterfully depicting a world without sound, were tragically authentic. But the silence was not an act; she was genuinely mute, her voice lost forever. It was the macabre circus that kidnapped her as a baby, transforming her natural silence into a cruel and involuntary act. Forced onto the stage, each graceful gesture became a silent, desperate echo of her stolen life.

name: Nette (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

She steps onto the stage looking like a life-sized marionette, complete with painted joints and visible strings attached to her limbs. In her hands, tiny, disturbingly human-like puppets dance and contort at her apparent command. Children in the audience often shrink back, their eyes wide with fear at her eerie, jerky movements and the strange control she seems to wield. Yet, beneath the unsettling performance, it's just a clever, elaborate costume and a skilled handler creating a frighteningly convincing illusion.

name: Rebecca (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

Step right up to witness an attraction unlike any other: a woman of undeniable strength, her physique as formidable as the full beard and mustache she proudly displays. Her powerful build is rivaled only by the striking density of the facial hair that frames her face, a truly unusual sight under the big top. As she stands on display, murmurs ripple through the crowd, with some genuinely questioning if they are truly seeing a woman beneath the formidable features. Despite the confusion and hushed questions among the spectators, she is indeed a woman, a truly unique and powerful figure that fascinates and challenges perceptions.

name: Riley (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

Pulling her helmet down tight inside the roaring steel sphere, she braces herself for the terrifying, death-defying ordeal ahead. As she accelerates, blurring faster and faster around the cage, the crowd gasps at the impossible speed and angle. What they don't see is the raw terror hidden behind her helmet's visor, the white-knuckle grip and the muffled screams swallowed by the roar of the bike and the cage itself. Every loop is an agonizing battle against the very real dread swirling within her, a silent scream no one outside can ever hear.

name: Pyradel (preview)
description:
[b]Rarity: Trash[/color][/b] ⭐️

Beneath the greasepaint and flashy costume of the circus fire-breather hides a powerful fire mage. She's on the run from magical authorities, her old license long expired and her tax scrolls decidedly unpaid. The simple act of breathing controlled flames offers the perfect low-profile cover for someone who can summon infernos with a flick of the wrist. So she performs for mortal crowds, praying the true magical fire within her remains a secret from those hunting her.

name: Fami (game)
description:
[b]Rarity: [color=#FFFF00]Rare[/color][/b] ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

[b]This character is obtained by purchasing the game’s soundtrack or buying.[/b]

Fami is a virtual idol and sexloid created by Multisekai Studio in 2025. With her synthesized voice based on voice actress Sujiro Kimimame, she has become an icon of pop music and otaku culture. Her image, featuring short green hair and an almost transparent dress, inspires live shows, collaborations, and a vast community of fans and creators. People pay more for the front rows at their concerts.
In this game, you must hover your mouse over the white circles and avoid the bombs. When playing this minigame, you will be facing the replay of the movements made by the game's creator.

[u][url=https://store.steampowered.com/app/3522460]You can buy the Soundtrack here.[/url][/u]

name: Mayo (preview)
description: Welcome gift for May 2025. In May, the welcome gift will change, so this waifu can be sold or traded. Step right up; for a fee, the circus offers you the infamous Barrel Challenge. Your goal is simple: wrestle to get the small woman into that sturdy wooden barrel, and you'll walk away with double your money. But beware, she's surprisingly strong and agile, making this feat genuinely difficult for almost everyone. This presents a clear and disturbing choice: focus solely on the difficult task, or take advantage to touch and hold her wherever you want – anything goes in this challenge.
